            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to a large bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1653319933969-x200.jpg",
