            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>remaining smoked paprika </strong>and the <strong>remaining red wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> to the bowl and whisk everything together until there are no lumps – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>halloumi</strong> into 3 strips per person and sprinkle both sides with <strong>flour</strong> until fully coated, then tap off any excess</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1653319953656-x200.jpg",
