            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> pitta bread[s]</strong> to a toaster for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>chopped cucumber </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p><p>Mix everything together – this is your <strong>yoghurt & cucumber salad</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining natural yoghurt </strong>with the<strong> mustard ketchup </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>yellow sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
