            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1653319978413-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your sandwich, slice open the <strong>warmed pitta </strong>and fill it with a dollop of <strong>yellow</strong> <strong>sauce</strong>, 2<strong> tomato rounds</strong>, a <strong>outer</strong> <strong>lettuce leaf</strong> and 3<strong> battered halloumi slices </strong>– this is your<strong> Greek-style battered halloumi sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>yoghurt & cucumber salad </strong>and <strong>garlic fries </strong>to the side with the<strong> remaining yellow sauce</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
